Description: Pryme NV is a Company based in the Netherlands. The Company is engaged in recycling of plastics using chemical technologies. Prymeâ€™s activities concentrate on converting plastic waste into petrochemical products using chemical processes, mainly pyrolysis process. The technology involves decomposing polymers by exposing plastic waste to high temperatures. The final products of the process can be reused as a fuel or are delivered to petrochemical plants to become polyethylene and polypropylene. The Company purchases plastics and other raw materials and markets the processâ€™ finished products. Other objectivities of the Company include constructing, developing and operating factories that are involved in the reuse of plastics.
